</p></supplementary-material><table-wrap id="T5" orientation="portrait" position="float"><label>Table 5</label><caption><p>Calculation of average cost of dexmedetomidine study treatment per day</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>Price of dexmedetomidine:</bold> 200&#x02009;&#x000b5;g/2&#x02009;mL, 1 box = five 2&#x02009;mL ampoules</td><td valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>CHF</bold></td><td valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>143.24</bold></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>Price of dexmedetomidine per ampoule</bold></td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>CHF</bold></td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>28.65</bold></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>Patient weight:</bold> assumed average</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>kg</bold></td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>80.00</bold></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>Duration of dexmedetomidine infusion:</bold> 20:00&#x02013;06:00</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>hrs</bold></td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>10.00</bold></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>Average dose of dexmedetomidine per hour:</bold> Bolus of 0.7&#x02009;&#x000b5;g/kg/hour, followed by 0.2&#x02013;1.4&#x02009;&#x000b5;g/kg/hour for desired level of sedation</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"/><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"/></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
